4
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:11,820
Koichi: It’s reimi!

5
00:00:11,850 --> 00:00:14,360
Reimi: Hey, Rohan, did you
take the pictures in this album?

6
00:00:14,390 --> 00:00:15,820
Rohan: I did. Why?

7
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:17,890
Reimi: I assume there’s a reason
this one is marked.

8
00:00:17,930 --> 00:00:19,430
What’s so special about it?

9
00:00:19,460 --> 00:00:22,330
