on this little boy.

10
00:00:22,360 --> 00:00:24,830
Rohan: Oh, yeah.

11
00:00:24,870 --> 00:00:26,770
I’m not too concerned with him.

12
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,840
he seemed to be
sneaking around the area,

13
00:00:28,870 --> 00:00:30,440
so I thought i’d document him.

14
00:00:30,470 --> 00:00:31,740
Reimi: But look.

15
00:00:31,770 --> 00:00:33,980
The boy’s name
is hayato kawajiri.

16
00:00:34,010 --> 00:00:36,640
He has the same surname
as this man.

17
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:38,810
- ( Koichi gasps )
- Rohan: Really? He does?

18
00:00:38,850 --> 00:00:40,820
