30
00:01:13,510 --> 00:01:15,650
i could have sworn
it was hayato in the bath.

31
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:18,420
Honestly, what are we
going to do with that boy?

32
00:01:18,450 --> 00:01:20,360
Look at this place.
His clothes are scattered

33
00:01:20,390 --> 00:01:21,860
around the hallway
like a bomb went off.

34
00:01:21,890 --> 00:01:23,860
I wish he’d take after you
a little bit more.

35
00:01:23,890 --> 00:01:25,560
He can be such a slob.

36
00:01:25,590 --> 00:01:29,060
Not to mention he’s ignoring me.
Though, if I know him,

37
00:01:29,100 --> 00:01:32,070
he’s probably reading manga
with his headphones on again.

38
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:33,840
( Gasps ) Honey, what happened?

39
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:36,440
