41
00:01:37,770 --> 00:01:39,370
You don’t want it
to get infected.

42
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,380
Eh? Eh?!

43
00:01:42,410 --> 00:01:44,780
kira: No,
i’ll take care of it myself.

44
00:01:44,810 --> 00:01:47,420
I just need a simple bandage.

45
00:01:47,450 --> 00:01:48,880
I can handle that.

46
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,350
Shinobu: Oh. Uh...

47
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:54,490
