66
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:58,890
That said, Rohan-sensei
thinks he’s onto something.

67
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,820
Josuke: I agree.
A grade-school kid

68
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:02,890
taking videos of his dad
on the down-low

