00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,830
sends up some serious red flags.

70
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:07,100
Koichi: We’re talking about
meeting up tomorrow morning.

71
00:03:07,130 --> 00:03:09,060
Once we’ve gone through
everything, we’ll head over

72
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:11,430
to hayato kawajiri’s house
together.

73
00:03:11,470 --> 00:03:13,970
Rohan-sensei said he’s already
figured out the address.

74
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,600
( Josuke chuckles )

75
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:17,810
that artsy asshole
doesn’t miss a beat, does he?

76
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,110
Josuke: Well, count me in.

77
00:03:19,140 --> 00:03:21,580
Oh, and I should ask
okuyasu, right?

78
00:03:21,610 --> 00:03:24,850
And jotaro, too.
Can’t forget about him.

79
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:27,750
Koichi: You can leave getting
in touch with Mr. Jotaro to me.

80
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:29,950
All right, we’ll see you
tomorrow at 8:30 A.M.

81
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,990
just look
for the big Pepsi sign.

82
00:03:32,020 --> 00:03:33,590
Josuke: Right. Got it.

83
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:35,660
Pepsi at 8:30.

84
00:03:35,690 --> 00:03:37,860
That means i’m gonna
be late for school.

85
00:03:37,890 --> 00:03:40,760
Even so, if things pan out
the way Rohan hopes,

86
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:43,060
it’ll be worth the tardy slip.

87
00:03:45,170 --> 00:03:48,100
♪

88
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:50,470
( Kira shudders )

89
00:03:50,510 --> 00:03:51,840
Shinobu: Are you okay?

90
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:53,980
I can tell there’s
something wrong, sweetie.

91
00:03:54,010 --> 00:03:55,680
You’re all pale and sweaty.

92
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:58,110
Kira: It’s nothing.
I’m perfectly fine.

93
00:03:58,150 --> 00:04:02,150
I’m just in some pain, is all.
I did just slam my fingers.

94
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:04,750
Now please, go downstairs,
and make some tea.

95
00:04:04,790 --> 00:04:07,220
I’ll be right behind you.

96
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:09,660
( Shinobu gasps )

97
00:04:09,690 --> 00:04:11,690
( Sighs ) Okay, dear.

98
00:04:12,990 --> 00:04:15,160
i know this is
gonna sound totally random,

99
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,600
but, well, I don’t know.

100
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:19,970
You’ve had this vibe,
like you’ll live forever.

101
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,140
( Kira shudders )

102
00:04:21,170 --> 00:04:24,040
Shinobu: The tea’ll
be ready soon.

103
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:29,080
( Door creaks )

104
00:04:29,110 --> 00:04:30,240
Yoshihiro: Huh?

105
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:32,550
( Kira shuddering )

106
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,790
Hayato: If you so much
as lay a single finger on me,

107
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:39,720
your whole cover
will be blown sky-high!

108
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:41,660
Stay the hell away
from me and my mom!

109
00:04:41,690 --> 00:04:44,090
It’s non-negotiable.
You got that?!

110
00:04:44,130 --> 00:04:46,490
stay away,
or I reveal everything!

111
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:50,800
Kira: You’re adorably naive!

112
00:04:50,830 --> 00:04:53,000
As if i’d let
someone find me out!

113
00:04:53,030 --> 00:04:55,100
- ( Trigger clicks )
- ( Boom )

114
00:04:57,910 --> 00:04:59,740
Yoshihiro: Getting rid
of that hayato brat

115
00:04:59,770 --> 00:05:01,280
was the very height
of foolishness.

116
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:03,180
You, of all people,
should have known that.

117
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:05,910
Kira: Quiet. I’m trying
to think of a way out of this.

118
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:08,950
Yoshihiro: Don’t waste time.
It’s too late for that now.

119
00:05:08,980 --> 00:05:11,790
You did a remarkable job
of making it look

120
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:13,790
as though he fell
and hit his head,

121
00:05:13,820 --> 00:05:16,120
but your timing
really couldn’t have been worse.

122
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,830
Rohan kishibe has already begun

123
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:20,130
his investigation
into hayato kawajiri.

124
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,700
They don’t know for sure yet

125
00:05:21,730 --> 00:05:24,630
that kosaku kawajiri
is yoshikage Kira,

126
00:05:24,670 --> 00:05:27,800
but they’re coming here tomorrow
to find out once and for all.

127
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:30,870
( Kira gasps )

128
00:05:30,910 --> 00:05:32,140
Yoshihiro: Son,
you mustn’t remain

129
00:05:32,170 --> 00:05:33,810
in this house a minute longer.

130
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:36,540
Kira: Will you stop talking?
I’m trying to think!

131
00:05:39,050 --> 00:05:41,050
( Yoshihiro blubbers )

132
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:43,920
Even when you were a boy,
when things didn’t go your way

133
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:45,890
and you felt the world
was against you,

134
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:49,260
you’d always bite your nails
’til your fingers were raw.

135
00:05:49,290 --> 00:05:50,590
( Kira murmuring )

136
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:52,790
Yoshihiro: My poor, sweet boy.

137
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:55,600
oh, the misery
you must be suffering.

138
00:05:57,900 --> 00:06:00,270
we’ve run out
of options here, kiddo.

139
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:03,270
you must leave this
wretched town behind for good!

140
00:06:03,300 --> 00:06:05,870
If you get out now,
you still have a chance

141
00:06:05,910 --> 00:06:08,680
to escape and hold on
to your anonymity.

142
00:06:08,710 --> 00:06:10,250
( Gasps )

143
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:12,110
Kira: Are you
seriously asking me

144
00:06:12,150 --> 00:06:14,220
to run away and abandon morioh?!

145
00:06:14,250 --> 00:06:17,020
living every moment
in excruciating secrecy is one

146
00:06:17,050 --> 00:06:19,890
of the most horrible experiences
a person can go through,

147
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:22,060
and I refuse
to go back to that hell!

148
00:06:22,090 --> 00:06:25,230
i swear I will
never leave this town.

149
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:27,230
( Yoshihiro gasps )

150
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:29,200
( Kira gasping )

151
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:34,640
What the hell?!

152
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:36,840
Yoshihiro: The arrow
moved on its own!

153
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:38,740
but I swear
I didn’t do anything!

154
00:06:38,770 --> 00:06:41,180
I wasn’t even touching it!

155
00:06:41,210 --> 00:06:42,880
Kira: Gah!

156
00:06:42,910 --> 00:06:44,150
What’s it doing?

157
00:06:45,810 --> 00:06:47,680
( Gasps )

158
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,980
Yoshihiro: No! Yoshikage!

159
00:06:50,020 --> 00:06:51,950
( Kira gagging )

160
00:06:59,460 --> 00:07:01,860
♪

161
00:07:01,900 --> 00:07:04,830
Shinobu: Hayato! Hayato?!

162
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:07,170
just how long
are you gonna sleep in?

163
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,170
It’s time to get up and--eh?

164
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:15,840
Hayato, why didn’t you tell me
you were out of bed?

165
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:16,850
You startled me.

166
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,880
Come down for breakfast.

167
00:07:18,910 --> 00:07:20,850
And answer when I call you.

168
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:28,120
hayato: I had
a terrible night’s sleep.

169
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:31,730
That jerkface imposter found out
I witnessed one of his murders

170
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,960
and assaulted me.

171
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:37,100
For now, i’ve made sure he can’t
do anything to hurt me or mom,

172
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:38,900
but that’s a temporary solution.

173
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:42,870
He’ll find a way around that.

174
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,710
- ( Kira humming a tune )
- ( Hayato gasps )

175
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:49,280
♪

176
00:08:01,260 --> 00:08:03,290
Yoshihiro: I don’t understand.

177
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,960
what in the world’s
gotten into you, yoshikage?

178
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,870
You’ve been acting strange
since last night.

179
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,470
Don’t ignore me!

180
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,770
I don’t know why,
but Rohan kishibe

181
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,840
is now keen on snooping
around hayato kawajiri!

182
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,340
We’ve run out of time, son.

183
00:08:19,370 --> 00:08:21,840
they’re coming
to search the house tomorrow!

184
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:24,510
( Kira chuckles )
There’s no cause for alarm.

185
00:08:24,550 --> 00:08:27,120
Yoshihiro: B-but, yoshikage!

186
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:33,390
kira: My deadly queen
has acquired a third ability.

187
00:08:33,420 --> 00:08:34,860
Yoshihiro: Huh?

188
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:42,330
What’s going on here?

189
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,830
♪

190
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:45,200
What could have happened
to make you

191
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:47,540
so lackadaisical
all of a sudden?

192
00:08:47,570 --> 00:08:50,170
announcer:
...Miso-marinated cow tongue.

193
00:08:50,210 --> 00:08:53,080
( Anchor coughs )

194
00:08:53,110 --> 00:08:54,340
You’re kidding!

195
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:56,440
Why didn’t you say
we were on the air?!

196
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:59,450
Good morning, all. It’s 7:55,

197
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,980
time for today’s
prefectural weather report.

198
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:04,050
today we’ll be
enjoying sunny skies...

199
00:09:04,090 --> 00:09:06,390
- ( Telephone rings )
- Shinobu: Hayato!

200
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:09,560
Hayato, are you listening?
Answer the phone!

201
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:10,990
( Telephone ringing )

202
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:13,290
Hayato: His attitude
has completely changed

203
00:09:13,330 --> 00:09:15,460
since that bath last night.

204
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:17,800
what happened
between now and then?

205
00:09:17,830 --> 00:09:19,200
( Telephone ringing )

206
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:21,800
Shinobu: Hayato,
what are you doing?

207
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:24,910
the damn phone isn’t
gonna answer itself, you know!

208
00:09:24,940 --> 00:09:26,040
( Gasps )

209
00:09:27,340 --> 00:09:28,510
( Shrieks )

210
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:30,510
My favorite China tea set!

211
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:31,580
( Hayato gasps )

212
00:09:31,610 --> 00:09:33,280
Shinobu: This is
all your fault!

213
00:09:33,310 --> 00:09:34,580
Why do you ignore me?!

214
00:09:34,620 --> 00:09:36,420
Don’t you have any respect
for your mother?

215
00:09:36,450 --> 00:09:39,990
Admit it! You only see me as
a nuisance who gets in the way!

216
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:41,960
Well, fine! I’m done!

217
00:09:41,990 --> 00:09:42,990
- ( Hayato gasps )
- ( Telephone ringing )

218
00:09:43,020 --> 00:09:44,390
Kira: Now, now.

219
00:09:44,430 --> 00:09:46,530
Let’s not start the day
with an argument.

220
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:48,530
- hayato: Huh?
- Kira: If it can’t be fixed,

221
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,100
i’ll buy you another one.

222
00:09:50,130 --> 00:09:52,930
This is the kawajiri residence.

223
00:09:52,970 --> 00:09:55,340
No, i’m afraid not.

224
00:09:55,370 --> 00:09:57,940
It was a wrong number.
that’s all.

225
00:09:57,970 --> 00:10:00,910
and hayato’s
going through a quiet phase.

226
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:02,340
No need to fret.

227
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:03,350
( Hayato stammering )

228
00:10:03,380 --> 00:10:05,010
Kira: We’re a family.

229
00:10:05,050 --> 00:10:07,920
We should support each other,
not tear each other down.

230
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:09,380
Let’s all work on that.

231
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:11,620
Speaking of work,
I should get going.

232
00:10:11,650 --> 00:10:15,220
But before I head off,
i’d like to steal a kiss.

233
00:10:15,260 --> 00:10:16,420
( Shinobu gasps )

234
00:10:16,460 --> 00:10:19,030
- Kira: Have a nice day.
- shinobu: Huh?

235
00:10:19,060 --> 00:10:20,330
( Hayato gasps )

236
00:10:23,570 --> 00:10:25,200
( Shinobu gasps )

237
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:29,970
( Hayato gasps )

238
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:40,210
Thank god. He took off.

239
00:10:40,250 --> 00:10:42,020
Kira: No, i’m right here.

240
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:46,090
why don’t we
walk together for a bit?

241
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,290
( Hayato shuddering )

242
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:50,260
♪

243
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:54,200
one moment,
i’m in the throes of despair.

244
00:10:54,230 --> 00:10:56,260
Now i’m on top of the world.

245
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:58,530
So much has happened
so very quickly.

246
00:10:58,570 --> 00:11:01,900
It’s been an absolute
whirlwind of emotion.

247
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:04,170
But now, at long last,
i’ll be able

248
00:11:04,210 --> 00:11:06,640
to live a life
free of worry and anxiety.

249
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:09,080
You really put the pressure on
last night,

